Package: ggdesign
Title: Making It Easier To Use ggplot2 Outputs In Graphic Design Software
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Martin", , "chrisjmartin03@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package that complements and extends ggplot2, adding functions 
  which make it easier to use ggplot2 outputs in graphic design software. It 
  helps the use to output ggplot charts in a way that makes them easier to use 
  in vector editing software, such as Illustrator, Figma and Affinity Designer. 
